THIS FILE IS A PLACEHOLDER — the real ONNX model is not included.

Please download or copy the Piper model binary to:

  ./okktrainer/ai/models/piper/en_US-ryan-high.onnx

The Docker setup mounts ./okktrainer/ai/models into the container as /models (read-only).
Ensure the file is the correct Piper ONNX model expected by your TTS pipeline.
